metadata.description: **Become a collector. Minting is live here:** ***https://cryptoadz.art.*** *First time offered: AI-generated CrypToadz oil masterpieces.*  CrypToadz stands among the most highly valued and coveted NFT collections.  The rarest Toadz fetch hundreds of thousands of dollars or more.  Even “floor” Toadz sell for tens of thousands. For the first time, you can mint these AI-generated oil paintings of the full CrypToadz collection.  Employing over two dozen AI technologies, this gorgeous collection allows connoisseurs to enjoy CrypToadz as never before.  Mint before they’re gone, then sell, trade, collect, or use however you would like during this era of explosive metaverse growth. Only one minting is available for each of the 6,969 CrypToadz, with every owner receiving an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain.
